reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars BEST LEGGINGS EVERY MADE
reviews.reviewText: By far the best leggings I have ever owned! The material feels like butter on your skin. It holds everything in, are not see through bending over standing up, or trying to stretch them out. They hold your tummy in nicely, make your butt look amazing, and hides any cellulite you may have. I have cellulite, big hips and booty and it holds everything in and makes it look smooth! I will buy in every color!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Really comfortable lululemon dupe!
reviews.reviewText: I’ve been trying to find the perfect lulu dupe for me and out of all the leggings I’ve tried these are my favorite. First of all they have a big inside pocket in the tummy high rise section which I love. And the placement of the seams are just what I’m looking for, super flattering. They are buttery smooth and fit wonderfully. They are compression like so if you don’t like it fitting too tight maybe size up. I’m normally a size medium and these are a medium but they are on the tighter side. But they are perfect for working out of everyday life.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice quality and feel thicker than aligns
reviews.reviewText: I bought these for my Fiancé and she really likes them. I've been hunting for something that can rival her favorite Aligns and this is a really nice fallback. They are thicker but almost indistinguishable in outward appearance. They feel nice to the touch. The waist line is slightly higher. They manufacturer said they have switched from Poly blend to Nylon blend because of feedback, so if you think you're getting Polyester blend don't be surprised, you probably wont.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great quality, but one pair arrived with marks on them
reviews.reviewText: Love the quality and fit of these leggings, but one pair arrived with stains/marks on them. It won’t keep me from ordering more though. These have great stretch, thickness, and support. Very comfortable and they aren’t shiny like work out leggings so perfect for a casual outfit!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best leggings EVER 😍
reviews.reviewText: These leggings are a new staple in my closet! They’re thin and lightweight but not at all see through. I am a plus sized gal, and these are THICK GIRL FRIENDLY! They wash well and keep their buttery smooth texture after multiple wears. They look small when they come out of the package but they STRETCH and provide the perfect high waist fit. Sadly the pair I got has no pockets but they’re so wonderful that I hardly even mind! I’ve already ordered a few more colors!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars I hate the new fabric blend
reviews.reviewText: These leggings were my absolute FAVORITE. I’ve bought dozens of them. But now over the past few months when I have tried to buy new pairs in the black 28 inseam or the black 7/8 leggings they are sending ones made with Nylon instead of the polyester blend. I also double check before ordering that the fabric on the item I select is the polyester blend, not nylon.The nylon fabric isn’t comfortable or soft. It seems to attract all kinds of lint. The nylon fabric blend also sucks if you have thick thighs that rub together when you walk. It feels like the fabric gets caught together and doesn’t glide like the polyester blend fabric does.I’m disappointed they aren’t sending the correct item and at this point I will be looking at other brands of leggings that offer better fabric/fit options.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect Blend of Comfort and Functionality!
reviews.reviewText: I purchase these leggings a year ago and recently purchased another pair. My obsession with this brand began with their biker shorts and I have never looked back. These are the best leggings and biker shorts I have found!Positive Aspects:I am thrilled with my purchase! These leggings have exceeded my expectations in several ways:1. Buttery Soft Comfort:The fabric of these leggings is incredibly soft and smooth, making them a joy to wear. It feels like a second skin and provides the perfect level of comfort during workouts.2. High-Waisted Perfection:The high-waisted design is fantastic. It provides excellent support without feeling restrictive, and it stays in place during various exercises. No constant readjusting needed!3. 4-Way Stretch:The 4-way stretch is a game-changer! Whether I'm stretching, doing yoga, or going for a run, these leggings move with me effortlessly. It gives me the flexibility I need for my diverse workout routine.4. Squat Proof Assurance:I tested the squat-proof claim, and I'm happy to report that these leggings passed with flying colors. No transparency issues at all, even during deep squats. This feature is a game-changer for anyone serious about their workouts.5. Convenient Pockets:The addition of pockets is a thoughtful touch. I can easily slip my phone or keys into the side pockets during my runs, eliminating the need for an extra armband or carrying accessories.6. Durability:After several washes, the leggings still look brand new. The quality is outstanding, and I'm confident these will be a staple in my activewear wardrobe for a long time.Conclusion:In conclusion, the Sunzel Leggings for Women are a stellar find. They combine comfort, functionality, and durability seamlessly. Whether you're hitting the gym or doing a home workout, these leggings will become your go-to choice. I highly recommend them to anyone in search of the perfect workout leggings!Note to Potential Buyers:These fit true to size. Overall, these leggings are a fantastic investment in both comfort and style.

reviews.reviewText: These are the perfect blend of Beyond Yoga & Alo, for a fraction of the price. Really nice high rise with a super soft fabric that still holds you in & stays in place through every activity
so soft & cozy and V shape is so faltering. great quality

I've found my new go-to workout companion in the Sunzel Workout Leggings! Let me start by saying, these leggings are a dream in terms of comfort.The fabric? Oh, it's like a second skin – buttery soft and smooth against the skin. The 4-way stretch is a game-changer, allowing for unrestricted movement during workouts or even just lounging around. And squat-proof? Absolutely! I've tested these through various yoga poses and gym sessions, and they've passed with flying colors.Now, let's talk about that high waist. It's not just a style choice; it's a confidence booster! The high-rise design holds everything in place comfortably, offering support without feeling constrictive. Plus, the way these leggings hug my curves is simply flattering – especially for the derrière!Speaking of which, these leggings are magical in the 'making my butt look good' department. The way they sculpt and lift is honestly impressive. I've had compliments galore, and let's just say these leggings have become my secret weapon for a confidence boost.Washing? Easy peasy. They hold up remarkably well, maintaining their shape and softness even after multiple washes.In conclusion, the Sunzel Workout Leggings are a comfort lover's dream and a confidence seeker's best friend. They're versatile, supportive, and yes, they do wonders for that backside! Whether you're hitting the gym or just lounging, these leggings are an absolute must-have in any wardrobe.
